quran[9{c,v,t}:
34,23,aur khuda ke haan ( kisi ke liye ) sifarish faida nah day gi magar is ke liye jis ke baray mein woh ijazat bakhshay. yahan taq ke jab un ke dilon se iztiraab daur kardiya jaye ga to kahin ge tumahray perwar-digaar nekiya farmaya hai. ( farishtay ) kahin ge ke haq ( farmaya hai ) aur woh aliiiii rutba aur graami qader hai
34,24,pucho ke tum ko asmano aur zameen se kon rizaq deta hai? kaho ke khuda aur hum ya tum ( ya to ) seedhay raste par hain ya Sarih gumraahi mein
34,25,keh do ke nah hamaray gunaaho ki tum se prssh hogi aur nah tumahray aamaal ki hum se prssh hogi
34,26,keh do ke hamara perwar-digaar hum ko jama kere ga phir hamaray darmain insaaf ke sath faisla kardey ga. aur woh khoob faisla karne wala aur sahib ilm hai
34,27,kaho ke mujhe woh log to dikhao jin ko tum ne shareek ( khuda ) bana kar is ke sath mila rakha hai. koi nahi balkay wohi ( akela ) khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
34,28,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko tamam logon ke liye khushkhabri sunanay wala aur darane wala bana kar bheja hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
34,29,aur kehte hain agar tum sach kehte ho to yeh ( qayamat ka ) wada kab wuqoo mein aeye ga
34,30,keh do ke tum se aik din ka wada hai jis se nah aik gharri peechay rahoge aur nah agay brhho ge
34,31,aur jo kafir hain woh kehte hain ke hum nah to is quran ko manen ge aur nah un ( kitabon ) ko jo un se pehlay ki hain aur kash ( un ) zaalmon ko tum is waqt dekho jab yeh apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray hon ge aur aik dosray se radukad kar rahay hon ge. jo log kamzor samjhay jatay they woh barray logon se kahin ge ke agar tum nah hotay to hum zaroor momin ho jatay
